data.description: Nestled in a tranquil neighborhood, this charming home boasts a brand-new roof that adds a touch of modernity to its exterior. Adorned with sleek solar panels, the residence not only exudes eco-friendliness but also harnesses the power of the sun for energy efficiency. Stepping inside, the gleaming hardwood flooring creates a warm and inviting atmosphere, seamlessly connecting each room. The kitchen is a culinary haven with state-of-the-art appliances, offering both functionality and style. A finished basement provides additional living space, perfect for entertainment or relaxation, while the expansive yard space outside completes the picture, promising endless possibilities for outdoor activities and gatherings.  Subject to Third Party Approval. Short Sale.
